section.def:
carriageway (車路) has
            the meaning assigned to it by regulation 2 of the Road Traffic (Traffic
            Control) Regulations (Cap. 374 sub. leg. G);

central reservation (中央分道帶) has the meaning assigned to it by regulation 2 of the Road
            Traffic (Traffic Control) Regulations (Cap. 374 sub. leg.
                G);

traffic lane (行車綫)
            has the meaning assigned to it by regulation 2 of the Road Traffic (Traffic
            Control) Regulations (Cap. 374 sub. leg. G);

paragraph.content:
any vehicle referred to in regulation 4(2)(c)(i) or (ii);
                        and (49
                            of 2000 s. 10)

subsection.def:
permitted user (許可使用者) has the
                meaning given by regulation 12(4) of the Road Traffic (Traffic Control)
                Regulations (Cap. 374 sub. leg. G);
